    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Male figures, usually nude or only partly clad, used as supports or apparent supports. They are occasionally found on furniture from the 16th century onwards.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
